e notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n <p><em><code>UIEventInit</code> dictionary 亦接受 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\" title=\"EventInit\"><code>EventInit</code></a> dictionary 所接受的參數。</em></p>\n </div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規格","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#dom-uievent-uievent","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.UIEvent.UIEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器支援度","id":"瀏覽器支援度","isH3":false,"query":"api.UIEvent.UIEvent","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"延伸閱讀","title":"延伸閱讀","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a>，此 constructer 所建立的 object 的 interface。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"語法","id":"語法"},{"text":"規格","id":"specifications"},{"text":"瀏覽器支援度","id":"瀏覽器支援度"},{"text":"延伸閱讀","id":"延伸閱讀"}],"summary":"UIEvent() constructor 是用來建立新的 UIEvent。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"UIEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"UIEvent()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"UIEvent()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/uievent/uievent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/uievent/uievent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/UIEvent","title":"UIEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent","title":"UIEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"UIEvent() - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}